From: OpenWrt HC-EN101 Build <build@local>
Date: Thu, 7 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: add device tree for Huaichen Telecom HC-EN101

Add device tree support for Huaichen Telecom HC-EN101 (TE1104H0)
router based on NXP LS1012A SoC.

Boot flow:
- QSPI NOR: RCW + U-Boot (bootloader only, not modified by OpenWrt)
- eMMC: kernel (fitImage on p1 ext4) + rootfs (squashfs on p2)

Hardware:
- RAM: ~990MB DDR @ 0x80000000
- 2x PFE Ethernet with RealTek RTL8211F PHY (RGMII)
- eMMC boot storage (DG400 7.3GiB)
- QSPI NOR: Macronix MX25U12835F 16MB (bootloader only)

Signed-off-by: OpenWrt HC-EN101 Build <build@local>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile            |  1 +
 .../boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls1012a-hc-en101.dts   |  1 +
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls1012a-hc-en101.dts

--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile
@@ -6,6 +6,7 @@
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_LAYERSCAPE) += fsl-ls1012a-frdm.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_LAYERSCAPE) += fsl-ls1012a-frwy.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_LAYERSCAPE) += fsl-ls1012a-qds.dtb
+dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_LAYERSCAPE) += fsl-ls1012a-hc-en101.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_LAYERSCAPE) += fsl-ls1012a-rdb.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_LAYERSCAPE) += fsl-ls1028a-qds.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_LAYERSCAPE) += fsl-ls1028a-rdb.dtb
-- 
